                    <desc>
                      Numbered quires: quires 1–7 numbered. Quire 9 (begins on f. 63) is numbered as 10. It seem that the quires numbered 8 and 9 have been lost. The numbering then continues with 10–14 (quires 9–13)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
