                      erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#3v #5v #7v #8r #14r" facs="006 008 010 016">3v, 5v, 7v, 8r, 14r, </locus>, etc.);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#36v #37r" facs="039">36v, 37r</locus>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
